kind of a coughing, but musical sound.</i>

999
01:01:14,890 --> 01:01:17,226
<i>And I went outside,
and I saw some men</i>

1000
01:01:17,309 --> 01:01:20,145
<i>that were trying to repair a pothole.</i>

1001
01:01:20,229 --> 01:01:22,522
<i>And they had an air hammer
that they were trying to use,</i>

1002
01:01:22,606 --> 01:01:26,944
<i>but it had gotten a rock
caught in the rubber hose...</i>

1003
01:01:27,027 --> 01:01:28,862
<i>which fed the air to the hammer.</i>

1004
01:01:28,946 --> 01:01:31,490
<i>And so as they activated the hammer,</i>

1005
01:01:31,573 --> 01:01:33,909
<i>they were actually playing
a funny musical instrument.</i>

1006
01:01:33,992 --> 01:01:38,205
<i>I said, "Please, don't fix it. Let me go
get my recorder. I'll be right back."</i>

1007
01:01:38,288 --> 01:01:43,210
<i>Obviously they looked at me like I was
