1008
01:01:43,293 --> 01:01:46,546
<i>I came back a few moments later
with my recorder.</i>

1009
01:01:46,630 --> 01:01:49,466
<i>We recorded
that funny air compressor...</i>

1010
01:01:49,549 --> 01:01:53,220
<i>and used it for the sounds
of the bikes shifting gears.</i>

1011
01:01:53,303 --> 01:01:55,973
<i>George Lucas came by to listen
to the speeder bike chase...</i>

1012
01:01:56,056 --> 01:01:58,267
<i>when I thought it had been completed,</i>

1013
01:01:58,350 --> 01:02:01,103
<i>and he sat through it-he hadn't
