1015
01:02:04,982 --> 01:02:07,067
<i>It didn't have
quite enough presence to it.</i>

1016
01:02:07,150 --> 01:02:09,820
<i>His suggestion was
that we put in the sound...</i>

1017
01:02:09,903 --> 01:02:14,074
<i>of snapping branches and leaves,
and the kind of noises you'd get...</i>

1018
01:02:14,157 --> 01:02:16,868
<i>if those bikes were really
zooming through the forest...</i>

1019
01:02:16,952 --> 01:02:20,205
<i>and clipping the edges of foliage
