1023
01:02:33,260 --> 01:02:36,763
<i>and we would ramp in those sounds
so there'd be a brief burst...</i>

1024
01:02:36,888 --> 01:02:39,683
<i>of just sticks and dirt noise and grit.</i>

1025
01:03:05,959 --> 01:03:07,961
LUCAS: <i>We started with the Ewoks...</i>

1026
01:03:08,045 --> 01:03:10,839
<i>who were,
in the original screenplay, Wookiees...</i>

1027
01:03:10,922 --> 01:03:13,592
<i>that I couldn't use
