1029
01:03:17,679 --> 01:03:20,097
<i>I needed to come up
with a primitive creature...</i>

1030
01:03:20,181 --> 01:03:25,186
<i>that was still using sticks and stones
and spears for weapons...</i>

1031
01:03:25,269 --> 01:03:27,480
<i>and lived in a primitive society...</i>

1032
01:03:27,563 --> 01:03:31,400
<i>that would be forced to take on
the highly technological Empire.</i>

1033
01:03:32,485 --> 01:03:37,573
<i>So, ultimately, I decided to keep
