1862
01:55:51,183 --> 01:55:52,601
<i>and when they're added to it.</i>

1863
01:55:53,018 --> 01:55:55,394
<i>But you can see there's a whole-
There's a style to it.</i>

1864
01:55:55,478 --> 01:55:56,538
<i>There's a whole life of its own...</i>

1865
01:55:56,562 --> 01:55:58,002
<i>that the animator would bring to it.</i>

1866
01:55:58,981 --> 01:56:01,418
