1944
02:00:37,133 --> 02:00:41,220
<i>that's, you know,
a real threat to someone.</i>

1945
02:00:41,304 --> 02:00:44,014
<i>But on the other hand,
there's cartoon issues in it,</i>

1946
02:00:44,097 --> 02:00:47,517
<i>which is somebody can fall
