1947
02:00:47,601 --> 02:00:50,020
<i>or jump an incredible distance...</i>

1948
02:00:50,103 --> 02:00:54,441
<i>when at other times they can't run fast
enough to get away from something.</i>

1949
02:00:54,566 --> 02:00:57,444
<i>You know. It's filled with
these kind of dramatic ironies...</i>

1950
02:00:57,527 --> 02:01:01,740
<i>that one has to be really careful
